{"tid":1559652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好畀林奠擾亂視線！黑警曾經開真槍！","createTime":"2019-09-11T02:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T02:30:46.000Z","uid":299258,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"169a0797eba79528c788302393b9d1591c8d2893","tid":1559652,"uid":299258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"林奠呢個惡毒嘅犯婦人，假扮徹回送中條例，其實係要等立法會複會再處理，安插兩個自己人去監警會就當回應左成立獨立調查委員會嘅訴求，以為咁樣就呃到全世界！另外，831肯定都係有預謀搞出嚟。我無證據講831有無死人，但我好肯定政府係不斷擾亂視線，想開好多條線令焦模糊！我個人覺得要平反要揭露嘅一定要繼續。要從民事索償更加要落力！向美國尋求協助更加要唔好手軟！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但，大定唔好忘記！和理非示威有黑警扮示威者掟汽油彈！開真槍！隨身攜帶胡椒彈槍以作襲擊！聲稱需要執法但無表明警察身分及出示委任證！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以上所講嘅都係十分嚴重嘅罪行！大家千祈唔好畀單一事件模糊視線！繼續追究！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvMHC3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqvMHC3Q.jpg&h=0135b8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmwMkhb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmwMkhb.jpg&h=d42be4e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRYCrXc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRYCrXc.jpg&h=daf17386&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kukhrXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkukhrXd.jpg&h=edc0687a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"572ae863956fe5813b8854f4af03361bcfbfab5e","tid":1559652,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:04:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42275bdfd72e4c227c3ff3f1381cb8e29614babf","tid":1559652,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fabf01460efc05dd82c5b9f3d33f999c6906cf16","tid":1559652,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"160c8fdcf069f0f9d894426f38316b3b2298ed57","tid":1559652,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"